<div style="padding-left: 2rem; padding-right: 2rem; padding-top: 1rem; padding-bottom: 2rem;">
    <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h1 class="h4" style="color: #164098;">Treasury Bills Participation</h1>
        <ol style="text-align: left;">
            <li>The SBP holds a Primary Auction of Market Treasury Bills every fortnight</li>
            <li>The Auction Calendar for upcoming auction dates are available on the SBP website and can be viewed by <u><b>selecting “Primary Auction – Auction Calendar”</b></u> from the menu bar</li>
            <li>Once you have determined which auction date you would like to participate in please select <u><b>“Primary Auction – Non Competitive Bid Form”</b></u> to submit your bid</li>
            <li>The Non Competitive Bid Form requires you to make the following selections:</li>
            <ul>
                <li>Placement of Non Competitive Bids – Select Instrument which you would like to invest in from the drop down menu: Treasury Bills/Ijara Sukuk</li>
                <li>Auction Date – Select Auction Date: The nearest three “3” auction dates will be visible for you to select from. Please note that the last day for submission of a bid for to participate in an auction date will be 5 days before the scheduled auction date</li>
            </ul>
            <li>Your IPS Account Number and CNIC/NTN will be prefilled. Please verify and if any discrepancy please reach out to our TMU Department</li>
            <li>Select Maturity – options will depend upon the Instrument selected above since both Treasury Bills and Ijara Sukuk have different maturity profiles. For example you can select the duration to invest for in Treasury Bills for 3/6/12 months</li>
            <li>Insert Bid/Investment Amount – Please insert the amount you would like to invest in the selected Instrument and Maturity selected above</li>
            <ul style="list-style-type: none;"><u>Note :-</u>
                <li>Your account must have sufficient funds at the time of submitting bid</li>
            </ul>
            <li>Multiple Bids: You can divide your <u><b>portfolio and submit multiple bids</u></b>  across each Maturity available. Please click <u><b>“Add More”</u></b> and repeat the process</li>
            <li>If you would like to top up your account with funds please click <u><b>“?”</u></b> on the tool bar and select <u><b>“How to Invest”</u></b> to see details regarding the fund transfer process</li>
        </ol>
    </div>
</div>